In general, the public to Daxing airport have a variety of transportation options, the cost and time is also within a reasonable range.
From the perspective of trend development: Daxing Airport is positioned as a Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei transportation hub, so it is a little farther away from Beijing, but it has strengthened the radiation to Hebei and Tianjin, which has facilitated more people's travel and is of great significance to the economic development of Hebei and Tianjin.
