Pilot notification commitment system in the field of low-risk variety food production license, and delegate authority to the free trade zone for the handling of foreign enterprises' representative offices
On the 27th, the Shanghai Municipal Market Supervision Bureau and the Pudong New Area Government signed a working memorandum to launch 20 market supervision and reform measures, some of which are the first pilot in the country.
