According to the memorandum, the Shanghai market supervision department will support the registration of the Pudong New Area and the Shanghai Free Trade Pilot Zone in the enterprise name registration, handle the simple process and low-risk variety food production license, and partially approve the type of measuring instruments and other three areas of pilot notification commitment system, so that enterprises can enter more easily.
