After the reform, the approval link was reduced from the previous six links of "registration, acceptance, on-site verification, sample inspection, material review, approval and certification" to 3 links of "registration, acceptance, and approval of documents", and the completion time was shortened from 20 working days before the reform to the on-the-spot completion.
Taking into account the high degree of extrovertibility of Pudong's economy, the Shanghai market supervision department will delegate the registration authority of the permanent representative office of foreign (regional) enterprises to the Shanghai Free Trade Zone, which is convenient for enterprises to handle it nearby.
