Liu Kun, Minister of Finance: 67 central enterprises and financial institutions have transferred 861 billion yuan of state-owned funds to enrich the Social Security Fund.
Liu Kun, Minister of Finance, said on the 27th that as of now, 67 central enterprises and central financial institutions have completed the transfer of some state-owned capital to enrich the social security fund, with a total transfer of about 86.1 billion yuan of state-owned capital.
Liu Kun made the above statement at the deployment meeting of the national transfer of some state-owned capital to enrich the work of the Social Security Fund jointly convened by the Ministry of Finance, the Ministry of Human Resources and Social Security, and the SASAC on the same day.
"The transfer of some state-owned capital to enrich the social security fund is an important measure to reform and improve the basic pension insurance system, and it is a full manifestation of the generational fairness of the development results of state-owned enterprises and the intergenerational fairness of the basic pension insurance system, and is a policy measure based on the current and long-term."
In 2017, the State Council issued the "Implementation Plan for Transferring Some State-owned Capital to Enrichment Social Security Fund", requiring the selection of some central enterprises and some provinces to carry out pilot projects.
According to Liu Kun, the preliminary work of the transfer has achieved positive results.
At the central level, three batches of 67 central enterprises and central financial institutions have been transferred, with a total transfer of about 86.1 billion yuan of state-owned capital.
Among them, the transfer of central financial institutions by the Ministry of Finance to perform the duties of investors has been basically completed.
The transfer of central enterprises already has a certain scale.
At the local level, the pre-project of enterprise transfer has been carried out successively.
By the end of 2018, the pilot work in Zhejiang and Yunnan provinces had been basically completed, with 15.8 billion yuan and 18.5 billion yuan of state-owned capital respectively.
In addition to the pilot provinces, other provinces have also carried out the preparatory work for the transfer, laying the foundation for the next step of the transfer.
According to the joint notice issued by the Ministry of Finance, the Ministry of Human Resources and Social Security, the SASAC, the State Administration of Taxation and the Securities Regulatory Commission, the work of the central and local governments to enrich the social security fund with some state-owned capital was fully launched in 2019 and basically completed by the end of 2020.
The meeting held on the same day made specific arrangements for the comprehensive promotion and transfer of work.
The meeting stressed the need to complete the transfer work pragmatically and efficiently.
According to the schedule, the transfer work should be basically completed by the end of 2020.
Transfer the working time is tight, the task is heavy."
Liu Kun said that all regions and departments should carefully organize and carefully arrange to ensure that the transfer work is completed as required; solidly promote the work, accurately grasp the content of the transfer policy; strengthen communication and coordination, and solve difficult problems in a timely manner.
State-owned capital transfer to enrich the social security fund - starting from the starting point of "enriching the social security fund money bag", the destination is to provide strong support for pension security.
However, the author believes that this is not a simple equity "physical displacement", but opened the "mathematical addition".
On September 20, the Ministry of Finance, the Ministry of Human Resources and Social Security, the SASAC, the State Administration of Taxation, and the Securities Regulatory Commission jointly issued the "Notice on Comprehensively Promoting the Transfer of Some State-owned Capital to Strengthen the Work of the Social Security Fund", clarifying the timetable for the transfer of state-owned capital to the Social Security Fund, that is, the work of the central and local governments to enrich the Social Security Fund was fully promoted in 2019.
After the publication of the document, the Ministry of Finance and other departments have also implemented it quickly.
On September 25, the Ministry of Finance transferred 10% of the shares held by the Industrial and Commercial Bank and the Agricultural Bank to the Social Security Fund, and the total value of the two shares transferred exceeded 115 billion yuan.
According to the regulations, the Social Security Foundation and other undertakers, as financial investors, enjoy the right to income, dispose of and know the rights to be transferred to the state-owned equity.
The ICBC and the Agricultural Bank said in the announcement that this change in equity will not lead to changes in the controlling shareholders and actual controllers of the Bank.
In this regard, the author believes that similar state-owned enterprise equity transfer is not a simple change of equity ownership, but can stimulate a series of effects of "addition operations".
The first step of some state-owned capital transfer social security "admission results", naturally can reflect the state-owned enterprises for all, development results shared by all.
After years of reform and development, state-owned enterprises, especially central enterprises, are mostly in important industries and fields in China's economy, and the overall profitability is strong and stable.
Among them, leading enterprises continue to achieve better and bigger and stronger.
On July 10, the executive meeting of the State Council decided to fully promote the transfer of some state-owned capital to enrich the work of the Social Security Fund this year.
The Ministry of Finance immediately said that it will work with relevant departments, according to the deployment of the executive meeting of the State Council, to comprehensively promote the transfer of some state-owned capital to enrich the social security fund, fully reflect the intergenerational fairness of the basic pension insurance system and the sharing of the development results of state-owned enterprises.
The second step of the transfer of "addition results" is to enhance the sustainability of China's social security fund and further consolidate the foundation of the pension social security system.
With the aging of the population, China's social security funds are under pressure, and most of the state-owned capital, which has been transferred to the main body, has sustained profitability and dividend ability, which can not only effectively supplement the social security fund, but also provide the source of living water for the social security fund.
Some estimates show that for every transfer of state-owned capital of 3.8 percentage points, the proportion of contributions to basic pension insurance can be reduced by 1 percentage point.
The third step of the transfer, the "adhesion result", is to add a stabilizer to the capital market.
The transfer of the main body to obtain income is " dividend-based, auxiliary operation".
The Social Security Fund, as a financial investor of state-owned capital, does obtain equity dividend income.
However, as a value investor in the capital market, the Social Security Fund has a strong capital operation ability.
For the listed assets in state-owned capital, the participation of the social security fund in the shareholding will further optimize the corporate governance structure of listed companies, which is conducive to improving the operating level of enterprises and has a positive impact on listed companies and the capital market.
At the same time, as an investment vane, the improvement of the shareholding weight is conducive to further enhancing its influence in the market and playing a "stabilizer" role in the market.
In addition, it is also conducive to giving full play to the "value discovery" function of institutional investors and guiding investors to rational investment and value investment.
