"Panda Planet" belongs to the North Lake area, covering an area of 35 square kilometers, combined with industrial planning, will form a "1 + N + X" regional space structure.
One core attraction is the renovation and expansion project of the giant panda breeding research base; N cultural tourism consumption scenes are created, namely, panda town, permayuan, dream garden, etc.; X regional infrastructure facilities.
After the renovation and expansion of the Chengdu Giant Panda Breeding Research Base, the scale will reach 3,525 mu, which is generally positioned as a world-class giant panda protection demonstration site, and people and animals have a good time to share.
The park plans to accommodate 180 giant pandas and their accompanying animals (little panda and golden monkey).
